-new condition, unwashed, and with its original tags intact. Please include your order receipt and write your order # on the return package. Returns after 30 days of purchase will be reviewed and may be subject to a reduced refund. Single Item t-shirt returns have a flat fee of $10 for return shipping. Bundle returns may vary based on return postage cost. Exchanges may be completed free of charge. <BR>To initiate a return or exchange please contact hello@anydaycasual.com Refunds are typically issued within 5-10 days from the date of your return shipment. To greatly expedite the processing time of your return please notify our support team at hello@anydaycasual.com immediately after your return package has been placed in the mail. In this email include your order #, reason for return and confirmation of shipment (return tracking #).<BR>*We cannot reimburse return shipping or handling charges.**Please note that items purchased during special promotional periods or closeout sales are not eligible for refund. Exchanges may still be completed for promotional sale items. Please reach out to our support team at hello@anydaycasual.com to see if your purchase is eligible.
