any duties/taxes applied to your package. Customs policies vary by country; please contact your local customs office for more information.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-bkzZxe cSnsVU pf-7377"><button type="button" data-header-id="32bb6a3e-154f-4e6b-b377-d98620fb2438" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header" class="sc-dIUggk XavQL pf-154f"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>DO YOU OFFER ANY DISCOUNTS?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="32bb6a3e-154f-4e6b-b377-d98620fb2438" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-idOhPF kGntgQ pf-ce6b"><p class="sc-lcujXC epPudT pf-2438" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kIeTtH cnxSGb pf-20fb">Only one code promotion can be applied to each order. During a site-wide sale, all the code promotions are disabled.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-bkzZxe cSnsVU pf-8bad"><button type="button" data-header-id="9df75714-4e7b-49a5-8853-8badd27eb5aa" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header" class="sc-dIUggk XavQL pf-4e7b"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>ARE THERE SPECIAL CARE INSTRUCTIONS FOR ANYDAYCASUAL GARMENTS?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="9df75714-4e7b-49a5-8853-8badd27eb5aa" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-idOhPF kGntgQ pf-0853"><p class="sc-lcujXC epPudT pf-79a5" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kIeTtH cnxSGb pf-5714">To ensure that each piece retains that fresh out-of-the-pack look and feel, please follow the care instructions on the backside hem of each garment. We recommend machine washing cold and following up with hang drying.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-bkzZxe cSnsVU pf-66fa"><button type="button" data-header-id="7bc9d55f-7786-46e3-8fd2-66fac1acc1b8" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header" class="sc-dIUggk XavQL pf-7786"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>WHAT DO I DO IF MY ORDER IS INCORRECT OR DAMAGED?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="7bc9d55f-7786-46e3-8fd2-66fac1acc1b8" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-idOhPF kGntgQ pf-cfd2"><p class="sc-lcujXC epPudT pf-46e3" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kIeTtH cnxSGb pf-d55f">Please email hello@anydaycasual.com if the order you received was damaged or incorrect. We are passionate about our products and would love to help you out.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-bkzZxe cSnsVU pf-10b4"><button type="button" data-header-id="208151e1-c994-41c2-846b-10b4ebe68423" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header" class="sc-dIUggk XavQL pf-c994"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>WHEN WILL MY ORDER SHIP?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="208151e1-c994-41c2-846b-10b4ebe68423" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-idOhPF kGntgQ pf-446b"><p class="sc-lcujXC epPudT pf-a1c2" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kIeTtH cnxSGb pf-51e1">Typically, orders ship within 24 hours of purchase. Please allow 5-7 business days for standard shipping. Expedited shipping options are available with either 2 or 3-day shipping (selected during checkout). Orders placed after 1 pm on Friday may not ship until Monday morning.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-bkzZxe cSnsVU pf-a432"><button type="button" data-header-id="5e3e481c-5bfd-4373-be3b-a4324e2961b2" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header" class="sc-dIUggk XavQL pf-5bfd"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>WHERE DOES ANYDAYCASUAL SHIP FROM?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="5e3e481c-5bfd-4373-be3b-a4324e2961b2" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-idOhPF kGntgQ pf-3e3b"><p class="sc-lcujXC epPudT pf-9373" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kIeTtH cnxSGb pf-481c">All of our orders are processed and shipped from Milwaukee, Wisconsin.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-bkzZxe cSnsVU pf-2127"><button type="button" data-header-id="4fb37a50-8b72-4adc-8c75-2127cf1025e8" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header" class="sc-dIUggk XavQL pf-8b72"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>CAN I CHANGE MY ORDER AFTER I PLACE IT?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="4fb37a50-8b72-4adc-8c75-2127cf1025e8" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-idOhPF kGntgQ pf-cc75"><p class="sc-lcujXC epPudT pf-4adc" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kIeTtH cnxSGb pf-7a50">Can I change my order after I place it? Once an order has been placed it cannot be updated, this includes updates to shipping address, size, color, or style changes.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-bkzZxe cSnsVU pf-d663"><button type="button" data-header-id="2b43aaca-ee0e-4a76-bd0a-d663dc2a6659" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header" class="sc-dIUggk XavQL pf-ee0e"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>MY ORDER SAYS IT WAS DELIVERED BUT I DIDN’T RECEIVE IT</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="2b43aaca-ee0e-4a76-bd0a-d663dc2a6659" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-idOhPF kGntgQ pf-7d0a"><p class="sc-lcujXC epPudT pf-7a76" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kIeTtH cnxSGb pf-aaca">We know these things can be frustrating. Sometimes the carrier marks the package as "Delivered" prematurely. If you give it 3-5 business days, oftentimes the package will turn up. It's also helpful to ask your neighbors if the package was accidentally delivered to them. If there is still no trace of your delivery please contact your local post office, not the carrier hotline. The local post office will be able to provide you with details surrounding the delivery because they are given responsibility for the package once we have handed it to them for delivery. If the postal service is unable to assist you please contact us at hello@anydaycasual.com for additional support.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-bkzZxe cSnsVU pf-93a1"><button type="button" data-header-id="7a16e730-8d9b-46a0-b508-93a1d5d30c91" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header" class="sc-dIUggk XavQL pf-8d9b"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>WHAT FABRIC DOES ANYDAYCASUAL USE?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="7a16e730-8d9b-46a0-b508-93a1d5d30c91" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-idOhPF kGntgQ pf-f508"><p class="sc-lcujXC epPudT pf-06a0" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kIeTtH cnxSGb pf-e730">We believe everyday style should have exceptional quality which is why we have developed the best fabrics for you. Our 100% American pima cotton uses our signature Silk Stretch™ process which makes each t-shirt durable, breathable & buttery soft.
